WEBVTT

00:00.306 --> 00:02.853
The Smash Bros warrior knows no fear.

00:03.613 --> 00:06.488
He shall use Smash Run to master new moves like...

00:06.681 --> 00:08.011
..."Tornado uppercut!"

00:08.174 --> 00:10.192
He will grow more powerful with every battle...

00:10.267 --> 00:10.864
Yeah, baby!

00:11.433 --> 00:14.835
...until he's ready for his biggest battle yet.

00:15.475 --> 00:18.028
Settle it in Smash.

00:18.250 --> 00:19.089
What are you wearing?

00:20.601 --> 00:21.631
Little Mac.

00:21.901 --> 00:24.026
Settle it in Smash with Super Smash Bros...

00:24.141 --> 00:26.223
...now for the first time on Nintendo 3DS.

00:26.441 --> 00:27.556
Rated everyone, ten and up.

